{"tid":1145818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子鳳德邨攀窗墮樓亡　丈夫發覺制止不及","createTime":"2019-05-09T00:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T03:31:04.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c396090a10e052ff0c4d58ee10fbc09f25b7fd","tid":1145818,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:58:56.000Z","msg":"今日(9日)凌晨3時許，一名姓梁（61歲）女子，在黃大仙鳳德邨斑鳳樓6樓住所，趁家人不察攀窗墮樓，受傷倒臥簷篷上，其姓周（59歲）丈夫發現時，已制止不及，立即報警。消防員將女事主抬下，她已重創昏迷，由救護員送院搶救，可惜不治。警方向其夫調查，獲知女事主一向患病，因無檢獲遺書，正調查墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open 噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfmiIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=1fd76f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190509/mobile/bkn-20190509034106379-0509_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190509%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190509034106379-0509_00822_001.html&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfmiIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=bbb5cfc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190509/mobile/bkn-20190509034106379-0509_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"db822cb8bd5b400be5a9bed054d0a5db7225566e","tid":1145818,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:04:50.000Z","msg":"差佬:屌冇遺書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed248615e6830923954b27c2d9e04362f357116b","tid":1145818,"uid":211461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:07:24.000Z","msg":"應該快啲為安樂死立法<br />\n有啲病係每一秒都痛<br />\n又無合法途徑解脫<br />\n跳樓可能會砸死無辜途人"},{"pid":"273760c0c5fba485240c7503d8748762081a4259","ti